{"tid":1476982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PayPal宣布停止透過八達通「好易畀」增值","createTime":"2019-08-16T03:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:59:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45f0831fe9e826bb96c811732592846669f630d2","tid":1476982,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"支付工具PayPal宣布，10月1日起，停止透過八達通APP「好易畀」帳戶增值至PayPal帳戶，但仍指八達通卡仍是重要的合作夥伴，日後將繼續拓展合作空間。<br />\n<br />\nPayPal指出，由即日（8月15日）起，已不能連結PayPal帳戶到八達通「好易畀」帳戶；到10月1日，透過八達通「好易畀」增值服務將會終止。<br />\n<br />\nPayPal用家可繼續使用本地銀行轉帳為PayPal帳戶增值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2427516/【支付大戰】PayPal宣布停止透過八達通「好易畀」增值\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2427516%2F%E3%80%90%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91PayPal%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%93%E7%95%80%E3%80%8D%E5%A2%9E%E5%80%BC&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=28b734c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2427516/【支付大戰】PayPal宣布停止透過八達通「好易畀」增值</a>"},{"pid":"939eb5c2f9e55f77d1d61f192be8b5220ffb6d8f","tid":1476982,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}